---
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-32">
  <!-- Gradient background glow -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="h-[600px] w-[600px] rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 text-center">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20 bg-blue-500/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-blue-400">
      <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
      </svg>
      Driven av GPT-4o Vision
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
      Se vad som ändrades
      <span class="block text-blue-500">— inte bara att något ändrades</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400 lg:text-xl">
      changebrief bevakar webbsidor och berättar med AI exakt vad som hände. Inga suddiga screenshots. Inga röda pixlar. Bara en tydlig mening.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA buttons -->
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <a
        href="#pricing"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/25 transition hover:bg-blue-500 hover:shadow-blue-500/40"
      >
        Kom igång gratis
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#how-it-works"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-slate-300 transition hover:border-slate-500 hover:text-white"
      >
        Se hur det funkar
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Demo mockup -->
    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 p-6 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></div>
          <div class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/60"></div>
          <div class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/60"></div>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-slate-500">changebrief.io/dashboard</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 rounded-lg bg-slate-950 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">competitor.se/pricing</span>
                <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400">Importance: 8/10</span>
              </div>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
                Acme Corp tog bort "Gratis i 14 dagar"-knappen och höjde Pro-priset från 299 kr till 349 kr/månad. Ny feature "AI Insights" tillagd i Enterprise-planen.
              </p>
              <span class="mt-2 inline-block text-xs text-slate-500">3 minuter sedan via Slack</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
